================================================================================
Regenerating the Third-Party Inventory
================================================================================

THIRD-PARTY.txt is regenerated by running:

    mvn org.codehaus.mojo:license-maven-plugin:add-third-party

The output is written to target/generated-sources/license/THIRD-PARTY.txt
and should be copied to the repository root when dependencies change.
